OL,6,FA woman has said she has been left
OL,7,Fmentally and physically broken after
OL,8,Fshe narrowly survived a head-on crash
OL,9,Fwith a drunk driver.
OL,11,FRachel Downes was involved in the
OL,12,Fcollision in 2021 which broke almost
OL,13,Fevery bone in her body.
OL,15,FShe was in a coma for more than three
OL,16,Fweeks and has no memory of the
OL,17,Faccident .
