OL,6,FTwo-and-a-half-years after the crash
OL,7,Fin Rugeley, Rachel's finally been able
OL,8,Fto rebuild her life and she hopes to
OL,9,Fraise awareness of the consequences of
OL,10,Fdrink-driving.
OL,12,FShe told ITV News Central: "I didn't
OL,13,Fthink I would be the victim of a drink
OL,14,Fdriver.
OL,16,F"I guess I naively assumed most people
OL,17,Fwere smarter than that now.
