OL,3,CWoman forced to use zimmer frame after
OL,4,Cbeing hit in drunk driver crash
OL,6,F"It's quite shocking to think that
OL,7,Falmost 11 o'clock in the morning
OL,8,Fsomeone had got in their car still
OL,9,Fover the limit."
OL,11,FThe driver that hit Rachel on the A51
OL,12,Fbypass in Rugeley was heading to a
OL,13,Ffast food restaurant with friends
OL,14,Fafter drinking the night before. He
OL,15,Fwas almost double the legal limit.
OL,17,FRachel was rushed to the Royal Stoke
OL,18,FHospital with multiple, serious
OL,19,Finjuries.
