OL,3,CWoman forced to use zimmer frame after
OL,4,Cbeing hit in drunk driver crash
OL,6,FShe said: "I needed to adjust back
OL,7,Finto walking properly, I had to adjust
OL,8,Fto going to the toilet again.
OL,10,F"I couldn't shower myself for a long
OL,11,Ftime. I couldn't do stairs, I had to
OL,12,Frelearn how to walk up stairs.
OL,14,F"I was 29 and I didn't think I would
OL,15,Fbe using like a zimmer frame at the
OL,16,Fage of 29 and I was and it was just
OL,17,Fabsolutely bizarre."
