OL,4,Cbeing hit in drunk driver crash
OL,6,FRebuilding her life and body has been
OL,7,Fan ongoing challenge for Rachel - she
OL,8,Fwas physically, but also mentally
OL,9,Fbroken.
OL,11,FShe said: "Everything just seemed to
OL,12,Fspiral so quickly. I don't like
OL,13,Fbelieve in fate or anything like that
OL,14,Fbut I started to question my own
OL,15,Fbelief system.
OL,17,F"Because I was like well, if there is
OL,18,Fa god why has this happened or if fate
OL,19,Fis a thing or if karma is a thing what
OL,20,Fhave I done that has meant that I have
OL,21,Fbeen dealt this hand."
