OL,6,FIn July 2023, the offending driver was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 28 months in prison.
OL,9,FRachel said: "I'm hoping by sharing
OL,10,Fthis that at least one person
OL,11,Fsomewhere will go 'actually yeah i've
OL,12,Fhad a few drinks last night, it's
OL,13,Fquite early in the morning, maybe I
OL,14,Fwon't go for a drive'.
OL,16,F"I don't want anybody to go through
OL,17,Fwhat I went through at all."
